Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.50,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}この国の 人気の観光スポットです まだ　誰も見たことのない その屋敷を　ひと目　見ようと 標高３７２２ｍの死火山 ククルーマウンテン
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.50,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Today is the tenth day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.47,0:02:10.48,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}でも　今は会えない。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.47,0:02:10.48,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's Goreinu. Sorry to keep you waiting. What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.48,0:02:12.98,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ごめんな…」。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.48,0:02:12.98,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Do you realize it'll soon have been 240 hours
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.99,0:02:23.98,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ゴン　クラピカ レオリオの３人は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.99,0:02:23.98,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Why not? Genthru's team is camping the starting point.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.98,0:02:29.96,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}少しずつではあるが 屋敷に近づいていた その頃…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.98,0:02:29.96,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We decided beforehand that they \Nwouldn't return to the game until I sent an all clear signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.07,0:02:41.46,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.07,0:02:41.46,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm holding on to all the valuable cards. Doesn't that betray that they have other allies?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.46,0:02:44.46,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.46,0:02:44.46,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They'll notice if none of the four \Nhave any important cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.48,0:02:54.04,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}) )
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.48,0:02:54.04,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They left the game at 3:05, ten days ago, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.04,0:02:57.49,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((それは　完璧に 仕留めたってこと？))
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.04,0:02:57.49,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yeah, in five more minutes, \Ntheir card data will be wiped.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.49,0:03:00.48,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((どうせ　どこかから　俺のこと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.49,0:03:00.48,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Essentially, they'll be out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.48,0:03:03.48,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}見張ってたんだろ？)) )
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.48,0:03:03.48,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}To be safe, we'll wait until 3:10.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.48,0:03:05.97,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.48,0:03:05.97,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But do you really think they've given up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.97,0:03:07.99,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.97,0:03:07.99,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.99,0:03:09.99,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.99,0:03:09.99,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Given that they took Battera and ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:17.96,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:17.96,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But they spent years collecting \Nthose ninety-six cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.98,0:03:22.98,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.98,0:03:22.98,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Also, I'm wondering why Battera \Nwould send his guards packing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.49,0:03:46.99,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.49,0:03:46.99,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yeah, we switched about thirty of their \Nninety-six cards with fakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.98,0:03:56.47,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}) )
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.98,0:03:56.47,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm the one actually holding \Nthe ninety-six cards. For such a cautious man, this is the \Nbiggest gamble of Tsezgerra's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.47,0:03:58.47,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.47,0:03:58.47,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So I want to make sure it pays off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.47,0:04:05.08,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((はい キルア様が　お留守の間に 執事見習として雇われました カナリアと申します))
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.47,0:04:05.08,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm sorry, but I won't be able to \Nhelp you face Genthru's crew. Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.08,0:04:07.48,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.08,0:04:07.48,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}When do you want us to give you the card?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.48,0:04:10.98,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((いいえ　気持だけで十分です キルア様))
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.48,0:04:10.98,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'll wait until you've defeated Genthru. Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.98,0:04:17.51,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((「様」とか　つけんなよ キルアでいいよ)) ((そうは　いきません 私は使用人))
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.98,0:04:17.51,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Accompany \N\NWarp all players within \N20 meters of caster to city \N(must have been visited) \Nor player of your choice \N(must have been met \Ninside the game). \N\N[SR][NORM] Now it's time to go after those kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.51,0:04:20.56,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.51,0:04:20.56,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It wasn't in the plan, but we can \Nget Patch of Shore from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.56,0:04:23.56,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.56,0:04:23.56,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}First, we need more copies of Accompany.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.47,0:04:31.99,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((お前 さっき　「暗歩」使っただろ))
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.47,0:04:31.99,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Where are you right now? Near Soufrabi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.99,0:04:33.49,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.99,0:04:33.49,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They're heading toward Masadora.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.49,0:04:38.48,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((相手に悟られないように 無音で歩く歩行術のことだよ))
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.49,0:04:38.48,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Once they're prepared, they'll come for you. Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.48,0:04:43.06,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((ゾルディック家では 暗殺術の基本中の基本として
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.48,0:04:43.06,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Absolutely. We have you guys to thank.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.06,0:04:44.98,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}最初に叩き込まれるんだ))
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.06,0:04:44.98,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We need more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.98,0:04:47.99,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((そうでしたか　多分
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.98,0:04:47.99,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But we have no choice. It'll depend on Gon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.99,0:04:54.47,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}流星街で育つうちに　自然と 身についたのだと思います)) )
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.99,0:04:54.47,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Gon! Did you let our conversation \Ndistract you and lose track?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.01,0:05:02.08,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.01,0:05:02.08,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Please explain what this is about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.08,0:05:08.97,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}) ((流星街は 何を捨てても許される場所))
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.08,0:05:08.97,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I realize that I was being intrusive, but I took a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.97,0:05:11.98,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((だから　マフィアとか 「幻影旅団」の団員とかには
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.97,0:05:11.98,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Your daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.98,0:05:14.98,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}その街の出身者が多いんです))
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.98,0:05:14.98,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Or perhaps your granddaughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.98,0:05:17.53,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.98,0:05:17.53,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}My lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.53,0:05:21.97,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((その時は 私が　ご案内しますよ)) )
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.53,0:05:21.97,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}She'd been hospitalized for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:31.51,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:31.51,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}A few days ago, she passed away in her sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.51,0:05:36.51,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}) )
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.51,0:05:36.51,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I suppose she didn't want people \Nthinking she wanted my money, because she returned every gift I gave her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.98,0:05:49.96,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((歩行速度に緩急をつけて 残像を見せているんだ))
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.98,0:05:49.96,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}this shoddy picture frame that I made myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.47,0:05:58.04,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}) ((侵入者のようですね それも　かなりの数の…))
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.47,0:05:58.04,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}All we ever needed was one other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:06:03.98,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}) ((ご主人様の命令で　今日だけは ミケは動きません))
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:06:03.98,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We swore that we would never be apart...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.98,0:06:09.97,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((私の実力の程を 確かめたいそうです)) )
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.98,0:06:09.97,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Until the accident that put her into a sleep from \Nwhich she'd never wake...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.51,0:06:19.96,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((ここから先は　手分けして 奴らの屋敷を探し出す)) )
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.51,0:06:19.96,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Indeed... She appeared to only be sleeping...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.48,0:06:27.97,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}) )
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.48,0:06:27.97,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That was when I heard about Greed Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.52,0:06:33.46,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((あなた達がいる場所は 私有地です))
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.52,0:06:33.46,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If I beat that game, I could obtain the one thing
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.46,0:06:41.47,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((断りなく立ち入ることは まかり通りません)) ((お前に 俺達が止められるのか？))
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.46,0:06:41.47,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Breath of Archangel \N\NAn angel that cures any \Nmortal injury or terminal \Nillness with one breath. \NBut angel only appears once. that I need most, like a dream come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.47,0:06:44.50,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((どう見ても お前に勝ち目は　ねえだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.47,0:06:44.50,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I was prepared to spend my \Nfortune on copies of that game.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:53.98,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まぁ　おとなしくしていれば 命だけは助けてやる)) ((その線を　一歩でも越えたら 実力で排除します))
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:53.98,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But it doesn't matter any longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.98,0:06:55.96,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.98,0:06:55.96,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It doesn't matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.96,0:07:04.57,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((ボスが出るまでもねえ！ 俺達に任せてください！)) ) ) )
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.96,0:07:04.57,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The kids have four copies of \NAccompany among them. We have six.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.48,0:07:11.98,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.48,0:07:11.98,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'll take the kid with spiky black hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.98,0:07:15.98,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}) )
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.98,0:07:15.98,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Assuming we need to resort to force.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.98,0:07:17.48,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.98,0:07:17.48,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Sub, take the slant-eyed kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.98,0:07:27.98,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.98,0:07:27.98,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What do you want? Don't be so hostile.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.48,0:07:49.48,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.48,0:07:49.48,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What is it? Interested now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.48,0:07:54.47,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}これだけ倒しても 息ひとつ乱れていないとは…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.48,0:07:54.47,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Stop! Talk from where you are! Yes, that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.47,0:07:57.51,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((お前も　ゾルディック家の １人なのか？))
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.47,0:07:57.51,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We must act like we're at a \Nsignificant disadvantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.51,0:08:01.96,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.51,0:08:01.96,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We have to convince them
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:05.98,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((あなた方の実力では ゾルディック家の人は　おろか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:05.98,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}that we're being forced into this position.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.98,0:08:08.49,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}執事の所にすら たどり着けません))
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.98,0:08:08.49,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's quite simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.49,0:08:14.48,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}) )
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.49,0:08:14.48,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We'll beat the game on everyone's behalf, \Nthen everyone returns to the real world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.48,0:08:17.03,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.48,0:08:17.03,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And we'll split Battera's reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.03,0:08:19.03,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.03,0:08:19.03,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I find that hard to believe. We've had a change of heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.47,0:08:22.97,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.47,0:08:22.97,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And Tsezgerra has already left the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.47,0:08:26.47,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.47,0:08:26.47,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But that doesn't prove that \Nhe agreed to your offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.47,0:08:28.97,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.47,0:08:28.97,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You have a valid point.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.98,0:08:32.48,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.98,0:08:32.48,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Then, what now? Do you want to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.49,0:08:42.99,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.49,0:08:42.99,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You've revealed your true colors. Book! Accompany on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.97,0:08:53.98,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((フッ…　ハンターとして お前のような小娘に 負けるわけにはいかねえ))
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.97,0:08:53.98,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Three more times.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.47,0:09:01.97,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.47,0:09:01.97,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}One more time... Return \N\NWarp to a city \Nof your choice. \N(Must be a city \Nyou have visited.) \N\N[LR][NORM]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.99,0:09:07.49,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.99,0:09:07.49,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Masadora?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.06,0:09:13.48,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}) )
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.06,0:09:13.48,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Are they trying to obtain more spell cards? They might try to escape to the \Nreal world through the port.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.48,0:09:14.98,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.48,0:09:14.98,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Accompany on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.97,0:09:34.46,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((ヒィ！　すまねえ！ 命だけは　お助けを！))
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.97,0:09:34.46,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They haven't been here. Did they head for the port?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.46,0:09:35.96,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.46,0:09:35.96,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Tsk, guess we have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.96,0:09:37.98,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.96,0:09:37.98,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Accompany on! Gon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.49,0:09:44.07,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.49,0:09:44.07,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Don't lose sight of them! We're out of Accompany cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.53,0:10:02.53,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.53,0:10:02.53,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We'll never let you have them! Everything's gone to plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.99,0:10:10.99,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.99,0:10:10.99,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If we have to hand over our \Ncards, we'd rather fight! Wait, Gon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.99,0:10:13.99,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.99,0:10:13.99,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Damn... Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.55,0:10:17.97,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.55,0:10:17.97,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Now we only need to separate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:21.97,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}) )
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:21.97,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Bisky, you run for it! B-But... Just run!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.97,0:10:25.47,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.97,0:10:25.47,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Wait! Hey, you aren't getting away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.97,0:10:30.47,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.97,0:10:30.47,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm counting on you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.48,0:10:50.01,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.48,0:10:50.01,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You know that I'm the Bomber?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.01,0:10:53.01,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.01,0:10:53.01,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I heard it from Tsezgerra.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.49,0:10:59.99,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.49,0:10:59.99,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.55,0:11:11.05,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ゴン…。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.55,0:11:11.05,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}There aren't too many people
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.52,0:11:34.53,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}大丈夫なの？ ああ　気絶しているだけだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.52,0:11:34.53,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Whoever surrenders first has \Nto give up all his cards. You seem to have the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.02,0:11:44.52,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うぅ…　起きな！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.02,0:11:44.52,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This is your last chance to make a deal. Otherwise, you're nothing more than a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.51,0:11:50.53,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ん？　あぁ　兄貴　おはよう。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.51,0:11:50.53,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'd rather die than hand \Nover my cards to a thief! You can kill me, but I still \Nwon't take out my binder!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.53,0:11:53.51,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}今　何時？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.53,0:11:53.51,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You're insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.51,0:11:57.07,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}いい気になるなよ　キル！ そんなぁ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.51,0:11:57.07,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And I don't mean my kind of insane. Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.07,0:12:01.02,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺　兄貴を刺しちゃったこと すっげぇ反省してるよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.07,0:12:01.02,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You have a deal. Book.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.02,0:12:04.02,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ごめん　悪かったよ　兄貴。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.02,0:12:04.02,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm holding one hundred thirty-one cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.02,0:12:06.52,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ウソつけ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.02,0:12:06.52,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I have ninety-seven of the restricted slot cards. I have one hundred and two cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:15.54,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}やっぱ　分かる？ うん！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:15.54,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Book. You have #2 and #75, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.54,0:12:19.11,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[TEL] チッ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.54,0:12:19.11,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yeah. Book.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.11,0:12:24.02,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}はい。 あぁ　ママ？　うんうん…。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.11,0:12:24.02,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That's all I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.03,0:12:28.50,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うん　分かった。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.03,0:12:28.50,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}An excellent show of Ren...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.50,0:12:35.04,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}キル！　お前の友達 とうとう 執事室の近くまで来たそうだぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.50,0:12:35.04,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But clearly, he has much \Nroom for improvement.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.04,0:12:42.11,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}フフフ…　どうする？　キル。 俺がママに頼めば　３人とも…。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.04,0:12:42.11,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Offense is the strongest defense. You're strong enough that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.01,0:12:46.02,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ミルキ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.01,0:12:46.02,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}a single explosion won't be \Nenough to finish you off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.02,0:12:50.52,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}３人に手を出したら…　殺すぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.02,0:12:50.52,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So stay on the attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.01,0:12:58.53,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}紹介が遅れましたね。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.01,0:12:58.53,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But his use of aura is sloppy at best.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.53,0:13:03.03,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}私は　キルアの母です この子は　カルト。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.53,0:13:03.03,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Not sure why he was so confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.52,0:13:10.51,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}キルアが俺達に会えないのは 何でですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.52,0:13:10.51,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}At this point, you're nowhere near his level. You won't be able to deal significant damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.51,0:13:14.01,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}独房にいるからです。 独房？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.51,0:13:14.01,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But continue to attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.01,0:13:19.03,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}キルは私を刺し　兄を刺し 家を飛び出しました。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.01,0:13:19.03,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Because he will still defeat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.55,0:13:27.51,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}キルは　自分のしたことを反省し 自ら戻って来ました。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.55,0:13:27.51,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You still haven't answered my question. Who told you about my power?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.51,0:13:31.51,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そして今は　自分の意思で 独房に入っています。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.51,0:13:31.51,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Well, it isn't important now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.51,0:13:40.02,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ですから　キルが いつ　そこから出て来るかは…。 まぁ！　お義父様ったら！ 何をなさるおつもり!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.51,0:13:40.02,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}My point is that I don't need my ability to deal with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.02,0:13:49.53,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}勝手なことをしないで！ せっかく戻って来たのに　もう!! 入るぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.02,0:13:49.53,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}All according to plan. Once he's seen how much stronger he is, we'll begin to lure him into our trap! Osu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.52,0:14:02.04,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}でも　ゼノじいちゃん こいつ　全然反省してないんだぜ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.52,0:14:02.04,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'll make him use his power...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.04,0:14:05.11,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}んなことは分かっとる。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.04,0:14:05.11,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'll carry out the plan afterwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.11,0:14:08.02,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}キル　もう行っていいぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.11,0:14:08.02,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Looks like you need a little more pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.08,0:14:28.04,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}だから　おとなしく 殴られてやったんだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.08,0:14:28.04,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Use your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.04,0:14:30.52,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.04,0:14:30.52,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I have a surprise for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.52,0:14:34.51,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}キル　シルバが呼んどるからな。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.52,0:14:34.51,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I see what you're thinking. I won't use it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.01,0:14:48.01,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うぅ！ クッソ！　大体　じいちゃんは キルアに甘過ぎるんだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.01,0:14:48.01,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Damned kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.01,0:14:51.01,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}だから あいつが　つけ上がるんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.01,0:14:51.01,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}She's faster than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:56.50,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あいつは特別だからな。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:56.50,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Book!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.50,0:15:01.50,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ミル　お前から見て キルアの力量は　どうだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.50,0:15:01.50,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}She should be out of teleportation spells. What's she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.50,0:15:05.07,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そりゃ　すごいよ。 ほう…。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.50,0:15:05.07,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}She used Transform to hide \Nit as a different card?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.07,0:15:06.61,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}才能だけなら
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.07,0:15:06.61,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Accompany on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.61,0:15:09.99,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}長いゾルディック家の歴史の中で ピカイチじゃない？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.61,0:15:09.99,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}To Soufrabi! Accompany?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.99,0:15:14.01,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それは　ママも認めてるし 俺も　そう思う。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.99,0:15:14.01,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.52,0:15:22.01,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}でも　暗殺者としては失格だな むらっ気があってさ。 「むらっ気」？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.52,0:15:22.01,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I don't get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.01,0:15:26.56,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}友達なんか　つくってる奴に ゾルディック家は継げないよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.01,0:15:26.56,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Why would you go to all this \Ntrouble to be alone with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.56,0:15:31.06,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}要するに　あいつは弱虫なんだよ 精神的にさ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.56,0:15:31.06,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}One reason... Because I didn't want to let you cry for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.52,0:15:36.00,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そういうことだな。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.52,0:15:36.00,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Huh? I have no idea what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:38.51,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ねっ　その点　俺は
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:38.51,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You're such a fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.51,0:15:42.53,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}依頼があれば いつでも誰でも始末するぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.51,0:15:42.53,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm telling you that I'm stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.00,0:15:53.02,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}超小型でさ メスの蚊に取り付けて その蚊がターゲットの血を 吸った瞬間に爆発するんだぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.00,0:15:53.02,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Damned brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.01,0:16:05.01,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お前は　頭はいいが バカなところが　玉にきずだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.01,0:16:05.01,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Your attacks are too weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.52,0:16:09.59,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あぁ…！ まったく　お義父様ったら！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.52,0:16:09.59,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You can't defeat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.10,0:16:15.53,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}私　急用ができましたので では　これで。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.10,0:16:15.53,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I won't hold back...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.53,0:16:17.03,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}待ってください！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.53,0:16:17.03,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So don't blame me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.53,0:16:22.52,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺達　まだ　しばらく この街にいます。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.53,0:16:22.52,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That's what I was going to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.52,0:16:25.00,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}キルアに　そう伝えてください。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.52,0:16:25.00,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I was being nice, so I let you hit me once.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.00,0:16:29.00,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}分かりました　言っておきましょう それでは。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.00,0:16:29.00,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Because I can't restrain myself when I revert.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.11,0:16:39.02,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あなた達　何？ キルアの友達だよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.11,0:16:39.02,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And I end up killing my opponents!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.02,0:16:47.02,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}はい　お母様。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.02,0:16:47.02,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Oh, you're alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.56,0:16:55.00,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}言っちゃあ何だが 薄気味悪い連中だな。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.56,0:16:55.00,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Why would you... hide your power?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.00,0:16:58.52,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}キルアが　自分から「会えない」 って言ったのもウソくせぇ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.00,0:16:58.52,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Two reasons... The ace up your sleeve should remain hidden...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.52,0:17:04.01,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ゴン　このまま戻るのは シャクだぜ。 無理にでも　ついて行かねえか？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.52,0:17:04.01,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And more than anything, I hate the way I look.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.01,0:17:10.55,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うん　でも　そうすると きっと彼女が　責任を とらされるような気がするから。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.01,0:17:10.55,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Too macho! Don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.55,0:17:13.10,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あっ　そっか…。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.55,0:17:13.10,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He can't hear me anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.02,0:17:21.53,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そこなら　屋敷に直接つながる 電話があるから
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.02,0:17:21.53,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I have a slight advantage in martial \Nskill and physical strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.53,0:17:25.51,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ゼノ様が　お出になられれば あるいは…。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.53,0:17:25.51,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But he has me beat in aura capacity.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.51,0:17:30.03,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ゼノ様って？ キルア様のおじい様です。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.51,0:17:30.03,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I probably won't be able to hurt \Nhim with any normal attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.01,0:17:45.52,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うん。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.01,0:17:45.52,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I can't afford to fool around.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.59,0:17:54.59,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そうか。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.59,0:17:54.59,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Wrong. Experiment #1...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.01,0:17:58.51,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}試験は　どうだった？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.01,0:17:58.51,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Lightning Palm! Lightning Palm
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.02,0:18:08.52,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}キル　こっちに来い。 えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.02,0:18:08.52,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Doesn't seem to be enough to knock him out. But I can immobilize him for a few seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.52,0:18:11.52,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お前の話を聞きたい。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.52,0:18:11.52,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Okay. Experiment #2...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.08,0:18:16.01,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}試験で　どんなことをして
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.08,0:18:16.01,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}A yo-yo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.01,0:18:19.53,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}誰と出会い　何を思ったのか。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.01,0:18:19.53,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.53,0:18:24.02,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}どんなことでもいい　教えてくれ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.53,0:18:24.02,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What's he up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.01,0:18:33.10,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お義父様ってば 私に　何の断りもなく…。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.01,0:18:33.10,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What's that thing made of?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.10,0:18:37.60,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あら　キルったら パパとばかり楽しそうに…。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.10,0:18:37.60,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This is a superalloy yo-yo my brother ordered.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.50,0:18:41.52,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}許せないわ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.50,0:18:41.52,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It weighs around fifty kilograms, so it packs quite a punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.52,0:18:46.03,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}でさ　そしたらゴンが 何て言ったと思う？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.52,0:18:46.03,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.51,0:18:52.50,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ハハハ…。 アハっ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.51,0:18:52.50,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.50,0:18:56.59,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}わがままだろ？ 面白い子だな。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.50,0:18:56.59,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Between the weight and centrifugal \Nforce, that really hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.59,0:19:01.02,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それで今度は　剣を眉間に 突きつけられたんだけどさ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.59,0:19:01.02,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He always leaves his right side exposed
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.02,0:19:02.99,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それでもゴンは…。 キル。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.02,0:19:02.99,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}when I attack a certain way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.99,0:19:14.00,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}えっ？ 友達に会いたいか？ 遠慮することはない　正直に言え。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.99,0:19:14.00,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If I take his yo-yo, leaving him empty-handed, he'll make the same mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:16.56,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}思えば…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:16.56,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}My chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.56,0:19:21.06,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お前と親子として 話をしたことなど　なかったな。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.56,0:19:21.06,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}There!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.50,0:19:26.02,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺が親に暗殺者として 育てられたように
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.50,0:19:26.02,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Time to crush you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.02,0:19:29.52,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お前にも それを強要してしまった。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.02,0:19:29.52,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.51,0:19:36.01,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺と　お前は違う お前が出て行くまで
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.51,0:19:36.01,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Did I forget to mention that I have two yo-yos?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.01,0:19:39.01,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そんな簡単なことに 気づかなかった。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.01,0:19:39.01,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Wow, you're still conscious?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.10,0:19:44.02,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お前は俺の子だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.10,0:19:44.02,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Did you know that when you kick me, you raise your \Nguarding arm on the other side?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.02,0:19:46.50,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}だが　お前は　お前だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.02,0:19:46.50,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You're creating your own blind spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.50,0:19:55.50,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}好きに生きろ。 疲れたら いつでも戻って来ればいい　なっ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.50,0:19:55.50,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He used my blind spot to pull \Nout a yo-yo and attack? Then your defensive habit...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.50,0:19:58.53,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}もう一度　聞く。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.50,0:19:58.53,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Was a fake to make you \Nkick me with your left leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.53,0:20:01.59,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}仲間に会いたいか？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.53,0:20:01.59,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And when you released your first yo-yo...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.59,0:20:05.52,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うん。 分かった。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.59,0:20:05.52,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I knew you picked up something to throw at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.52,0:20:08.01,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お前は　もう自由だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.52,0:20:08.01,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Why did you use Accompany to \Ndraw me away from the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.01,0:20:10.01,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}だが…。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.01,0:20:10.01,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}To make you focus on a one-on-one chance, \Nso you'd lose track of your surroundings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.03,0:20:15.00,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}一つだけ誓え。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.03,0:20:15.00,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I don't believe it..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.00,0:20:20.07,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}絶対に仲間を裏切るな　いいな。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.00,0:20:20.07,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You set three traps during that brief exchange?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.07,0:20:22.51,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うん。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.07,0:20:22.51,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Three? You must be joking...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.51,0:20:25.03,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}誓うよ　裏切らない。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.51,0:20:25.03,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Every move I made was a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.00,0:20:35.02,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}キル。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.00,0:20:35.02,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Both work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.02,0:20:43.03,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}無駄よ　３人は帰ったわ 独房に戻りなさい。 イヤだ　俺　行くよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.02,0:20:43.03,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Why won't you accept your fate?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.03,0:20:45.01,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}キル!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.03,0:20:45.01,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You can't beat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.01,0:20:47.01,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}はっ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.01,0:20:47.01,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.03,0:20:50.53,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}どけよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.03,0:20:50.53,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I haven't lost yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.51,0:20:58.56,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ハハハ　あぁ　キル
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.51,0:20:58.56,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I was mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.56,0:21:03.06,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何て冷たい目が できるようになったの。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.56,0:21:03.06,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I take back what I said. You are strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.52,0:21:16.51,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}一体　何を考えてるの？ せっかくキルが戻って来たのに！ しばらく　好きにさせとけよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.52,0:21:16.51,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This battle is mental, not physical.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.51,0:21:18.51,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ダメよ　何　言ってるの！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.51,0:21:18.51,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I must crush his will.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.51,0:21:23.55,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}キルが 立派な後継者になれるかどうか 今が一番大切な時期なのよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.51,0:21:23.55,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}His will to fight, his will to stand, his will to resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.55,0:21:26.62,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}分かってるじゃねえか　じゃあ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.55,0:21:26.62,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Otherwise, he'll never admit defeat...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.62,0:21:29.62,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}つべこべ言わずに黙ってろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.62,0:21:29.62,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}To win, I must swallow my \Npride and play it smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.02,0:21:36.01,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}フフフ…　いつか　必ず戻って来る。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.02,0:21:36.01,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Let me demonstrate that all your hard \Nwork and confidence mean nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.54,0:21:49.13,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}キルアを自由の身にしながら 必ず暗殺者として戻って来ると 確信するシルバ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.54,0:21:49.13,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The devilish man has unleashed his true power.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.13,0:21:53.53,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そして 執事室へと向かったゴン達は
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.13,0:21:53.53,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Can Gon emerge victorious?
